posting_body: ['Property Address', '1305 Grand Ave - 304 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Top Floor One Bedroom Apartment at Grand Heritage Apartments', 'This top-floor one-bedroom apartment features meticulously restored hardwood floors throughout.', 'French doors give the living and kitchen area the perfect amount of privacy while maintaining ample amounts of sunlight throughout the apartment.', 'The kitchen area is spacious and has an eat-in-style dining area large enough for an office space, or a table for meals.', 'The Grand Heritage Apartments offer the best of Grand Avenue living.', 'Just a short walk away from several local shops and restaurants, Grand Heritage boasts a location that is within easy reach of major highways, as well as public transportation.', 'You will love the convenience of the upscale grocery store and deli on the corner, as well as the plethora of delectable restaurants surrounding the area.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Secured Entry', 'Heat/Water/Trash Paid', 'Coinless Laundry On-Site', 'Fitness Center and Clubhouse Across the Street', 'Online Resident Portal - Rent Payments and Maintenance Requests', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,024.00', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
